         <abstract id="aspace_1aa637517cf46a3f162fa37584b47f7f">The records consist of correspondence, subject files, news clippings, photographs and sound recordings documenting the Yale Sheffield Scientific School Class of 1929 and its reunions.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <corpname identifier="dts_3e7cf2d1396a7dab9e0f38a16ec683ca7fbeab2a" source="naf">
