      <odd id="aspace_30214f84146f94e70d136daaed323ce7">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 10-B (YRG 10-B), Records of Sheffield Scientific School classes.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_fd92b5c9656accb898d61bff310dc844">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were donated by Howard Gambrill, 2004; family of Watson F. Kinney, 2008.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_839069057f7e3ab226ec976dda90bfe0">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Access to the materials is restricted. See Collection Contents for details.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_67de7cbccc5bd3a780056e85beb045d5">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Class of 1929, Sheffield Scientific School, Yale University, Records (RU 952). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_03c7f453ce46b261608bf7c089cd0195">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, subject files, news clippings, photographs and sound recordings documenting the Yale Sheffield Scientific School Class of 1929 and its reunions.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_fa5204ab5ec7275dec725ed948b8b317">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by accession.</p>  
      </arrangement>
